languages.text: Allows Fury Interceptors to be launched through {g|Encyclopedia:TorpedoLaunchersSpace}torpedo tubes{/g}. A Fury Interceptor wing consists of 4 attack crafts, each equipped with a heavy laser turret. ! Up to 2 wings of Fury Interceptors can be active at a time.

traits.locale_text: Allows to launch wing of Fury Interceptors through torpedo ports. Wing consist of 4 crafts equipped with heavy laser turrets. ! Can't have more than 2 wings active at once.
